name: ErrorMessage
comment:
The module contains helper functions for specific error messages.

@docs typeMismatch, internal, canNotInit, unexpectedMessageFromJs

values.name: canNotInit
values.comment: Return error message that given module could not be initialized with given item for given reason

values.name: internal
values.comment: Returns error message for internal error

values.name: typeMismatch
values.comment: Returns error message for type mismatch

values.name: unexpectedMessageFromJs
values.comment: Return internal error message about receiving unexpected message from JS
